Name: pichemist
Version: 2.1.1
Summary: Calculates the isoelectric point (pI) of a peptide/protein using the Henderson-Hasselbalch equation with the predicted pKa values of its amino acids.
Home-page: https://github.com/AstraZeneca/peptide-tools/tree/master/pIChemiSt
